title: Captain America v5 034 - Director's Cut (2008) (Minutemen-Zone)
description: After the original issue sold out, Marvel released this Director's Cut version of CA v5 34, in which The Winter Soldier takes on the mantle of the red and blue. A now classic story, as part of Brubaker's run, it is included for the sake of completeness and as a different look at the landmark issue. The splash page with the reveal of the new Cap is one of my favorites. Thanks to Minutemen-Zone for this great scan - please seed and enjoy! :-)
